    </Paragraph>
    <Paragraph FontFamily="Calibri" FontSize="14">
        Essential Gantt WPF Edition is a MS Project like Project Viewer with inbuilt Grid, Scheduling and Resource assignment control. It is designed to assist project managers in developing plans, assigning resources to the task, tracking task progress etc. 
		Some of the key features of Gantt Control are you can Increase / Decrease the Start / Finish Date of the Task by mouse dragging on the both sides of the Task, Drag and Drop the Task to any places within the row, Automatic data synchronization between Grid and Chart, etc.



    </Paragraph>
